Package: clbart
Title: Conditional Logistic Regression with BART
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jacob", "Englert", , "jacobenglert@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5416-3604"))
Description: Fit a Bayesian conditional logistic regression model with a single 
    regression coefficient that is allowed to vary across the covariate space 
    via the the Bayesian Additive Regression Trees (BART) framework.
